      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ALL THE SASS (7) charged out of the boxes with a fast early split and led throughout to score when a 1.75 lengths winner (22.59) over 400m at this track. Has good speed and can quickly clear the pack out wide. Great chance to get the job done again. ICE COOL BLUE (2) was big odds last time but gave a huge sight after a fast early split, grabbed late but holding on to a placing when a 1.75 lengths second (22.71) over 400m at this track. Smart beginner who should take advantage of the low draw. Will give a great sight again. LONG GULLY ASH (5) has been out of the placings at his last couple but on the winners' heels when placing three back (22.74) in a Invitation at this track. Has good speed and can quickly clear the tricky draw. Expected to bounce back to best. DAKOTA SHINE (3) is always hard to beat when he races at this trip.",
